data.description: This brick ranch on a fenced in corner lot was completely renovated from top to bottom in 2018 and shows much pride of ownership. Home has 4 Bedrooms, 2 baths with a large new open concept as you walk in. In 2018 renovations included new roof, windows, kitchen, baths, flooring, paint, fixtures throughout. No expense was spared in this renovation to include high-end cabinets, granite counters and stainless-steel appliances. Large breakfast bar island and new kitchen overlooking large living room and dining room area. A large primary bedroom with beautiful full bath and 2 closets (1 Walk-in). Second hall bath with ceramic tile tub surround.
